trans-unit.source: Represents an element that participates in composition.
trans-unit.target: 代表參與在組合中的項目。

trans-unit.source: Gets the display name of the composition element.
trans-unit.target: 取得複合元素的顯示名稱。

trans-unit.source: Implementers of this property should never return `null` or an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性的實作者應永遠不會傳回`null`或空字串 ("")。

trans-unit.source: The human-readable display name of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ICompositionElement"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 人類看得懂的顯示名稱<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ICompositionElement"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the composition element from which the current composition element originated.
trans-unit.target: 取得目前的複合項目所起始的組合項目。

trans-unit.source: The composition element from which the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ICompositionElement"></xref> originated, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ICompositionElement"></xref> is the root composition element.
trans-unit.target: 從中的複合項目目前<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ICompositionElement"></xref>源自，或<xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>如果<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ICompositionElement"></xref>是根複合項目。
